---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="FieldHealth Africa privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">

    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-white/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>FieldHealth Africa (<strong class="text-white">fieldhealthafrica.org</strong>) is operated personally by <strong class="text-white">Dr. Nzozone Henry Fomukong</strong>, District Medical Officer, Mamfe, Cameroon. References to "we", "us", or "our" in this policy refer to Dr. Nzozone Henry Fomukong as the data controller.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">For privacy-related enquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@fieldhealthafrica.org" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">hello@fieldhealthafrica.org</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">2. What information we collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We collect only the information you actively provide or that is generated by your use of the site:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4">
          <li><strong class="text-white">Contact and enquiry forms</strong> — name, email address, and message content when you submit the contact form or request a callback. Forms are processed by Formspree (see section 4).</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Free Library download gate</strong> — email address, provided when you request access to a free tool. Used only to deliver the download link and, if you opt in, to notify you of tool updates.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Pro Library purchases</strong> — payment data (card details, billing information) entered during checkout. This is handled directly by Paystack; we do not store your payment card details.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Newsletter subscription</strong> — email address, if you choose to subscribe via our Substack publication (<a href="https://drhenrynzozone.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">drhenrynzozone.substack.com</a>). Substack's own privacy policy governs that relationship.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Analytics data</strong> — aggregate page-view and session data collected by Google Analytics 4, if a GA4 measurement ID has been configured. This includes approximate location (country/city), device type, browser, and pages visited. No personally identifiable information is passed to GA4 under our configuration.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">3. How we use your information</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4">
          <li>To respond to your enquiries and messages.</li>
          <li>To deliver free-library tools you have requested.</li>
          <li>To process and fulfil Pro Library purchases.</li>
          <li>To understand how the site is used and improve it (analytics).</li>
          <li>To send update notifications about tools you have downloaded, if you opted in.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">4. Third-party processors</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We use the following services, each governed by their own privacy policy:</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] p-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Formspree (formspree.io)</p>
            <p>Processes form submissions (contact form, download gate). Data is transmitted to Formspree's servers in the United States. <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2">Formspree Privacy Policy →</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] p-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Paystack (paystack.com)</p>
            <p>Processes payments for Pro Library purchases. Card data is handled exclusively by Paystack and is subject to PCI-DSS compliance. <a href="https://paystack.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2">Paystack Privacy Policy →</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] p-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Netlify (netlify.com)</p>
            <p>Hosts and serves the website. Netlify may log request metadata (IP address, headers) for security and performance purposes. <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2">Netlify Privacy Policy →</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] p-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Google Analytics 4 (analytics.google.com)</p>
            <p>Collects aggregate usage data, loaded only when our GA4 measurement ID is active. You can opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] p-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Substack</p>
            <p>Manages our newsletter publication. If you subscribe, your email address is stored by Substack. <a href="https://substack.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2">Substack Privacy Policy →</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use a small number of cookies for analytics and form functionality. See our full <a href="/cookies" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">6. Data retention</h2>
        <p>Form submissions (contact, download gate) are retained in Formspree for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose of the request, and deleted upon request. Purchase records are retained as required by applicable financial and tax regulations. Analytics data is retained for 14 months (Google Analytics default). You can request deletion at any time by emailing us.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">7. Your rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1 pl-4">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten").</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict certain processing.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent.</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority (EU/EEA residents: your national data protection authority).</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@fieldhealthafrica.org" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">hello@fieldhealthafrica.org</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">8. Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>FieldHealth Africa is not directed at children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes. Continued use of the site after an update constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy questions or requests: <a href="mailto:hello@fieldhealthafrica.org" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">hello@fieldhealthafrica.org</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
